{"tid":459063,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先落麥當奴交稅, 比條靚妹激死","createTime":"2017-11-05T12:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T11:24:58.000Z","uid":44333,"like":22,"dislike":397,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f8287fd41ada98b9522dfe2004a13cb8b7a0a737","tid":459063,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"上幾個星期收到稅單<br />\n今日得閒就諗住落樓下麥當奴交稅<br />\n平時買垃圾食物都係用自助機<br />\n今次要交稅無計啦就排counter<br />\n排到我就唔撚多講啦 直接比張稅單佢話交稅<br />\n跟住counter條靚妹好似聽唔明我講乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一開始都唔怪佢<br />\n毛都未出齊未交過稅都唔出奇<br />\n我就指住稅單上面個bracode等佢入機啦<br />\n另一隻手都拎定疊金牛等佢<br />\n<br />\n點知條靚妹夠膽死話無得交<br />\n我嬲到喊<br />\n佢又企係度ON99咁<br />\n經理係後面見到就即刻走過黎<br />\n埋黎督左個moon幾下<br />\n數埋銀紙就收左張稅單比張收據我<br />\n好心交稅季節就教定D員工點做啦<br />\n生得可愛就可以乜撚都唔識咩"},{"pid":"3f50ac5009afd47ee4f2a701482cfe5a5fbac2f6","tid":459063,"uid":61409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"bba9262c1a922ee3327a94281b77efb355eb6109","tid":459063,"uid":49054,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢樣野。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5219229b16007be6de8073b5d6be7ae551607658","tid":459063,"uid":27289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:55:16.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。"},{"pid":"fc3bb53736d7d3c408a4b8ec53e62a25dd65f3e0","tid":459063,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c45a3b4599a3c5ac01ebe304e07afe00313ed83","tid":459063,"uid":51978,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"做乜啫你"},{"pid":"d107aff466438af711d7b7aa11fac87ccafb1dd0","tid":459063,"uid":71726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face